    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/4205021/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            语词的创造的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3225712">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3225712/" class="title-link">语词</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3225712"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/miao126/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4806921-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/miao126/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">qhors苗广飞</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-05-01"
      class="main-meta">2010-05-01 15:13:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3225712_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  语词是有政治性的，因为这些话不仅可以给予人以动力，还可以给人以一定的状态，因此这就是政治的变动，政治变革都是语词变革的一个引申，因此我们就可以通过词汇的变动-我们自己-来实现政治性。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3225712_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3225712_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
